saving face is a 2012 documentary film directed by sharmeen &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and daniel junge about acid attacks on women in pakistan . the film won an emmy award and the 2012 academy award for best documentary short subject , making its director , sharmeen &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , pakistan 's first oscar winner . the film was inspired from the life of acid victim &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , who committed suicide in 2012 .